There is nothing with greater power then that of love.  I can truley say this because I am in love and it is a state I never want to leave.  I am currently dating the perfect woman for me.  She has everything I have asked for and more.  I think she is the best, most beautiful, smartest, sexiest lady to ever exist.  You know you are in love when you have that feeling you have lost something when they are not around.  Then you start asking, "Pleas someone help me find what I have lost?" then you notice that there is only one other person that can help you out.  Well at this point you run around wondering what to do you change your mood you change your clothes you can even change your laugh, just to see if you can possibly find that thing that is missing from your life.  And finally when you are desperate and lonely you go to your house open the door and look inside and see something that was missing, your kit-kat bar.  I really do not make sense do I?
